#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2210
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwave; Script Files"
msgstr "&kwave; skriptfiler"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2211
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Structure"
msgstr "Allmän struktur"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A &kwave; <emphasis>script</emphasis> consists of a list of lines, where "
"each line can be:"
msgstr ""
"Ett &kwave;-<emphasis>skript</emphasis> består av en lista med rader, där "
"varje rad kan vara:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2217
#, no-c-format
msgid "a single <emphasis>command</emphasis>,"
msgstr "ett enstaka <emphasis>kommando</emphasis>,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"a <emphasis>command list</emphasis>, with two or more commands concatenated "
"by a <quote><token>;</token></quote>."
msgstr ""
"en <emphasis>kommandolista</emphasis>, med två eller flera kommandon "
"sammanfogade med ett <quote><token>;</token></quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2226
#, no-c-format
msgid "a <emphasis>comment</emphasis>,"
msgstr "en <emphasis>kommentar</emphasis>,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2229
#, no-c-format
msgid "a <emphasis>label</emphasis>"
msgstr "en <emphasis>markör</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2232
#, no-c-format
msgid "or an <emphasis>empty line</emphasis>, that contains white space only"
msgstr "eller en <emphasis>tom rad</emphasis>, som bara innehåller blanktecken"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2238
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comments and Empty Lines"
msgstr "Kommentarer och tomma rader"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All characters that follow a <quote><token>#</token></quote> (except when "
"used in quotes or when escaped) are treated as comments, they will be "
"silently ignored."
msgstr ""
"Alla tecken som följer ett <quote><token>#</token></quote> (utom när det "
"används inom citationstecken eller efter &bsol;) behandlas som kommentarer, "
"och ignoreras tyst."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lines that contain only white space or comments are ignored as well."
msgstr ""
"Rader som bara innehåller blanktecken eller kommentarer ignoreras också."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Termination"
msgstr "Avslutning"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A &kwave; script terminates either when all commands have been executed "
"successfully without an error or when a command has returned an error code. "
"There is no special command for aborting the execution of a script. If you "
"want to implement a possibility for the user to end a script, you can use "
"the command <quote><link linkend=\"cmd_sect_msgbox\"><command>msgbox</"
"command></link>(<parameter><replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>)</"
"quote>. This shows a message box with the two buttons <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> (which lets the script continue) and <guibutton>Cancel</"
"guibutton> (which returns an error code and stops the script)."
msgstr ""
"Ett &kwave;-skript avslutas antingen när alla kommandon har körts utan något "
"fel, eller när ett kommando har returnerat en felkod. Det finns inget "
"särskilt kommando för att avbryta körning av ett skript. Om du vill "
"implementera möjlighet för användaren att avsluta ett skript, kan du använda "
"kommandot <quote><link linkend=\"cmd_sect_msgbox\"><command>msgbox</"
"command></link>(<parameter><replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>)</"
"quote>. Det visar en meddelanderuta med de två knapparna <guibutton>Ok</"
"guibutton> (som låter skriptet fortsätta) och <guibutton>Avbryt</guibutton> "
"(som returnerar en felkod och stoppar skriptet)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Labels"
msgstr "Markörer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lines that consist only of an identifier, followed by a <quote><token>:</"
"token></quote> are treated <emphasis>labels</emphasis>. They can be "
"referenced later in the script by the special keyword <command>GOTO</"
"command> <footnote><para>Note: Please don't mix up the keyword "
"<quote><command>GOTO</command></quote> with the text command <quote><link "
"linkend=\"cmd_sect_goto\"><command>goto</command></link> "
"(<parameter><replaceable>position</replaceable></parameter>)</quote> ! </"
"para></footnote> , which makes the execution of the script continue at the "
"location of that label (see example below)."
msgstr ""
"Rader som bara består av en identifierare följt av ett <quote><token>:</"
"token></quote> behandlas som <emphasis>etiketter</emphasis>. De kan senare "
"refereras i skriptet med det särskilda nyckelordet <command>GOTO</command> "
"<footnote><para>Observera: Blanda inte ihop nyckelordet "
"<quote><command>GOTO</command></quote> med textkommandot <quote><link "
"linkend=\"cmd_sect_goto\"><command>goto</command></link> "
"(<parameter><replaceable>position</replaceable></parameter>)</quote>.</"
"para></footnote>, som gör att skriptet fortsätter köra på etikettens "
"position (se exemplet nedan)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A line that contains a label must not contain any other content (except "
"comments or white space) after the <quote><token>:</token></quote>."
msgstr ""
"En rad som innehåller en etikett får inte innehålla något annat (utom "
"kommentarer och blanktecken) efter <quote><token>:</token></quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "Exempel:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:2283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>start:</replaceable><literal>  # &lt;= this is a label</"
"literal>\n"
"            <literal>        # do something...</literal>\n"
"            <literal>        </literal><command>msgbox</"
"command>(<parameter>once again?</parameter>)\n"
"            <literal>        </literal><command>GOTO <parameter>start</"
"parameter></command>"
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>start:</replaceable><literal>  # &lt;= detta är en etikett</"
"literal>\n"
"            <literal>        # gör någonting ...</literal>\n"
"            <literal>        </literal><command>msgbox</"
"command>(<parameter>Igen?</parameter>)\n"
"            <literal>        </literal><command>GOTO <parameter>start</"
"parameter></command>"

